<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .policy-box {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .premium {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Policy Issued</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>
        
        <p>Congratulations! Your insurance policy has been successfully issued.</p>
        
        <div class="policy-box">
            <p><strong>Policy Number:</strong> {{policyNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Coverage Period:</strong> {{startDate}} to {{endDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Premium Amount:</strong> <span class="premium">RWF {{premiumAmount}}</span></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Your policy is now active and provides coverage for the specified period. Please keep this information for your records.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Starhawk Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

